<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fancy-n">fancy <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fænsi/    美 /'fænsi/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>想要；喜欢：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She has simply <strong>taken a fancy to</strong> the place.
她简直是爱上了这个地方。</p><footer>2013 福建</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She said she wanted a dog but it was only a <strong>passing fancy</strong>.
她说想要条狗，但那只是一时的兴致而已。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="catch-take-sbs-fancy">catch / take sb's fancy</h3>
<p>1.<strong>引起某人的兴趣：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I could do without TV because few shows take my fancy.
我不看电视也行，因为很少有节目能引起我的兴趣。</p><footer>2010 安徽书面表达</footer></div></div>